# ovh_vps_automated_backup (Data Source)

Use this data source to retrieve information about automated backup settings for an OVHcloud VPS.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/data-sources/vps_automated_backup/example_1.tf"}}

## Argument Reference

* `service_name` - (Required) The service_name of your VPS.

## Attributes Reference

(See generated docs/data-sources/vps_automated_backup.md for the full attribute list.)

* `id` - The ID of the automated backup configuration.
* `cron_pattern` - The cron pattern for automated backups.
* `days_retention` - Number of days backups are retained.
* `enabled` - Whether automated backup is enabled.
* `max_capacity` - Maximum backup capacity.
* `state` - State of the automated backup.
